metadata.name: Nets II
metadata.description:
The Ocean Spirit, entangled.

‘Nets II’ is a photograph taken by Hasselblad photographer, David Teran. Audrey salvaged these fishing nets, swept onto the shores of Maui, and created this hand-sewn garment. 

This costume will be worn by the Ocean Spirit who dances for her freedom in ‘Oceans Apart’, an experimental film by filmmaker/performer Audrey Billups (pictured).

A portion of proceeds will be donated to Love the Sea, a Maui-based non-profit that removes plastic from remote beaches.

Includes unlockable content. Learn more: https://www.audreybillups.com/oceans-apart
